 role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533674\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533674\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xed1665702982139.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xed1665702982139.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xed1665702982139.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xed1665702982139\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Border Character Mnemonics\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The border character mnemonics define special characters used by Uniface in character mode to render frame borders for entities, area frames, lines, and so on. If these mnemonics are not defined, Uniface uses default characters, generally hyphens (-), vertical bars (|), and plus signs (+).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xed1665702982139__section_b1v_r4p_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d799658e51\">Arguments</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Mnemonics for Border Characters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Mnemonic</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Explanation</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bot_con</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border bottom connector. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bot_left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border bottom left corner. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bot_line</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border bottom line. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">bot_right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border bottom right corner. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">mid_con</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border middle connector. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">mid_left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border middle left corner. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">mid_line</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border middle line. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">mid_right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border middle right corner. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">top_con</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border top connector. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">top_left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border top left corner. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">top_line</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border top line. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">top_right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border top right corner. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">vert_left</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border left vertical. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">vert_mid</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border middle vertical. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">vert_right</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xed1665702982139__table_d5627e1_d5628e1_d5629e1__entry__2\">Border right vertical. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xed1665702982139__section_bwn_54p_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d799658e303\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xed1665702982139__p_d64217e1_d64218e1_d64219e1\">These characters are usually available in a device\n        character set. If they are defined as part of a particular character set, Uniface sends the\n        control codes to shift into this character set (if it is not already in this font), before\n        displaying or printing the character.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xed1665702982139__p_d64220e1_d64221e1_d64222e1\">For example, these mnemonics are defined as part of\n        character set 2 for the default display. The definition for this set in the USYSTERM device\n        translation table is shown below:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xed1665702982139__pre_epx_w4p_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">BEGIN_SET 2 begin special graphic set\n^esc(0 select special graphic set selection\n^^ reset reset characterset\n...\nl top_left map top left corner\nw top_con map top connector\nk top_right map top right corner\nq top_line map top line\nt mid_left map left middle corner\nn mid_con map middle connector\nu mid_right map right middle corner\nq mid_line map middle line\nm bot_left map bottom left corner\nv bot_con map bottom middle connector\nj bot_right map bottom right corner\nq bot_line map bottom line\nx vert_left map left vertical line\nx vert_mid map middle vertical line\nx vert_rightmap right vertical line\n...\nEND_SET\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xed1665702982139__p_d64223e1_d64224e1_d64225e1\">To produce a bottom left corner character (identified by\n        the <code class=\"ph codeph\">bot_left</code> mnemonic), Uniface first sends the codes associated with the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">select</code> mnemonic for character set 2, if this character set is not already\n        selected. It then sends the character code associated with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">bot_left</code>\n        mnemonic. For example, for the USYSTERM device, the following codes would be sent to the\n        device:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xed1665702982139__pre_fpx_w4p_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^027(0m\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533674\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533674\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Border Character Mnemonics Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Border Character Mnemonics The border character mnemonics define special characters used by Uniface in character mode to render frame borders for entities, area frames, lines, and so on. If these mnemonics are not defined, Uniface uses default characters, generally hyphens (-), vertical bars (|), and plus signs (+). Arguments Table 1. Mnemonics for Border Characters Mnemonic Explanation bot_con Border bottom connector. bot_left Border bottom left corner. bot_line Border bottom line. bot_right Border bottom right corner. mid_con Border middle connector. mid_left Border middle left corner. mid_line Border middle line. mid_right Border middle right corner. top_con Border top connector. top_left Border top left corner. top_line Border top line. top_right Border top right corner. vert_left Border left vertical. vert_mid Border middle vertical. vert_right Border right vertical. Description These characters are usually available in a device character set. If they are defined as part of a particular character set, Uniface sends the control codes to shift into this character set (if it is not already in this font), before displaying or printing the character. For example, these mnemonics are defined as part of character set 2 for the default display. The definition for this set in the USYSTERM device translation table is shown below: BEGIN_SET 2 begin special graphic set ^esc(0 select special graphic set selection ^^ reset reset characterset ... l top_left map top left corner w top_con map top connector k top_right map top right corner q top_line map top line t mid_left map left middle corner n mid_con map middle connector u mid_right map right middle corner q mid_line map middle line m bot_left map bottom left corner v bot_con map bottom middle connector j bot_right map bottom right corner q bot_line map bottom line x vert_left map left vertical line x vert_mid map middle vertical line x vert_rightmap right vertical line ... END_SET Copy To produce a bottom left corner character (identified by the bot_left mnemonic), Uniface first sends the codes associated with the select mnemonic for character set 2, if this character set is not already selected. It then sends the character code associated with the bot_left mnemonic. For example, for the USYSTERM device, the following codes would be sent to the device: ^027(0m Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}